The Insurance Institute for Highway
Safety elected Douglas Joyce as the chairman of its board of
directors.  Joyce, the president of Alfa Alliance Insurance Corp.,
succeeds Steven George, chief operations officer of AAA of
Northern California,  Nevada , and  Utah , who was the chairman
during 2011, the safety group said in a statement today on its
website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrea Ludtke in New York at 
